   \big| \prod\limits_{i=1}^n{x_{i}} \big|  = \prod\limits_{i=1}^n|{x_{i}}|   
   \big| \prod\limits_{i=1}^1{x_{i}} \big|  = |{x_{i}}|   
 \prod\limits_{i=1}^1|{x_{i}}| = |{x_{i}}|  
\prod_{i=1}^{0}x_i:=1
\prod_{i=1}^{n+1}x_i: =x_{n+1} \cdot\prod_{i=1}^{n}x_i
